# General structure
- folders: year / month /
- filename: yyyymmdd-hhmm-TITLE.md
- markdown
- tags

# Create

- diary create -> creates entry and shows file location (opens in vi?)
- flag:
    x title
    x date

# Tags
- Howto add tags?

# Search and show item
- ...SEARCHED TERM... (bold)
- x words before and after searched item (with searched item also bold)

# Search entries with certain tags

- flag:
    x tag

# Render

- flag:
    x year
    x yearmonth
    x tags
    x combinations?